data.description: Meticulously cared for and upgraded 3000sqft home awaits you and your family. Waking up in your primary bedroom you walk into your upgraded and gorgeous bathroom with spa tub, three showerhead large shower with tile throughout. You walk past the two large bedrooms one with a deck overlooking the quiet road your home is on. Descending the stairs you enter your chefs kitchen with granite counter tops, new stainless steel appliances, island and soft close cabinets. Your living room bay windows overlook the large fenced in back yard that has endless opportunities for your family or to entertain guests. Your bottom floor greets you with a spacious den, a sun room leading to your backyard, a large two car garage, bedroom, bath and laundry. Hardwired Cat8 ethernet cables run through the bottom level and upstairs bedroom promising high speed internet for WFH or gamers. The home boasts a new whole house fan, heat, central air, smart bluetooth water heater, and paint all done in 2022.
